  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT37">
<l>vāṉulavu tīvaḷi mākaṭal māporuppu</l>
<l>tāṉulavu veṅkatirum taṇmatiyu mēṉilavu</l>
<l>koṇṭaṟ peyarun ticaiyeṭṭuñ cūḻcciyu</l>
<l>maṇṭaṉ tirumā lakaippu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sky, the moving fire, the wind, the big seas, the big mountains,</l>
<l>The moving [sun] with hot rays, the cool moon,</l>
<l>the clouds that stay above, people, the eight quarters, [all] pervading [things],</l>
<l>The [cosmic] egg: [these] are the effects of Tirumāl’s will.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
